---
title: Chicken Thigh Pancit-Style Stir-Fry with Peppers
description: This take on a classic Filipino noodle stir-fry comes together in minutes! Broiled chicken strips are tossed into a hearty noodles, tender-crisp veggies coated with a salty-sweet sauce spiked with ginger and garlic. Satisfying and on the table in minutes!
